    "To create tabular data with both numbers and categorical values, the test used conditional Wasserstein GAN with gradient penalty.",
    "Auxiliary classifier loss was also increased by the team to force the model to precisely collect information from the underrepresented class.",
    "The GAN realizing for the demonstrated increased use of the theory of PacGAN with discriminator framework to accommodate m-packed samples as input instead of just a singular input.",
    "The mode collapse challenge of the conceptual scheme was alleviated by incorporating PacGAN framework.",
    "The studies were carried out to ensure that the model could be validated twice."
